      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个图来展示那次特别痛苦的功能分支合并过程。主线先有一个提交z，然后从main分出一个超长的特性分支，这个分支存在了很久才合并回去。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "commit z",
        "very-long-feature-branch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以主线第一个提交是z，然后立即分出那个长期分支。那这个分支的名字就叫'very-long-feature-branch'可以吗？还有，分支的顺序优先级需要特别设置吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "very-long-feature-branch",
        "order: 1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，名字就用very-long-feature-branch，order设成1让它显示在上方。然后切回main做提交a，这时候主线继续往前走了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "commit a",
        "checkout"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，主线现在有两个提交z和a，特性分支在z的位置。接下来特性分支上的开发是什么节奏？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit z",
        "commit a",
        "very-long-feature-branch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "特性分支上连续做了两个提交f和g，然后我们又切回main做了提交b。这时候两边是并行的状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit f",
        "commit g",
        "commit b",
        "checkout main"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认了，特性分支有f、g两个提交，主线现在有z、a、b三个提交。那最后是怎么合并的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit h",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最后特性分支又加了一个提交h，然后从main合并very-long-feature-branch。这个h提交是在合并前最后一刻加的，所以合并后主线会包含h。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit h",
        "merge very-long-feature-branch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。整个流程是：主线z→a→b，期间特性分支从z分出做f→g→h，最后main合并特性分支。这个图能清楚看出那个分支确实存在了很长时间。",
